Hi Anselm,

ScopePlusOneDecideRule was removed with Heritrix 3. Instead you=
 can do something similar using a `SurtPrefixedDecideRule` with an `alsoChe=
ckVia` property set to true.

For example, if you want to capture the equiv=
alent of scope plus one of http://example.com/* and of the SURT forms of yo=
ur seeds, you could use:

    &lt;bean class=3D&quot;org.archive.modules.deciderule=
s.surt.SurtPrefixedDecideRule&quot;&gt;
          &lt;property name=3D&quot;seedsAsSurtPref=
ixes&quot; value=3D&quot;true&quot; /&gt;
          &lt;property name=3D&quot;alsoCheckVia&quot; value=3D&quot;=
true&quot; /&gt;
          &lt;property name=3D&quot;surtsSourceFile&quot; value=3D&quot;&quot; /&gt;
       =
   &lt;property name=3D&quot;surtsDumpFile&quot; value=3D&quot;${launchId}/surts.dump&quot; /&gt;
   =
       &lt;property name=3D&quot;surtsSource&quot;&gt;
           &lt;bean class=3D&quot;org.archiv=
e.spring.ConfigString&quot;&gt;
            &lt;property name=3D&quot;value&quot;&gt;
             =
&lt;value&gt;
              +http://(com,example,
             &lt;/value&gt;
         =
   &lt;/property&gt;
           &lt;/bean&gt;
          &lt;/property&gt;
    &lt;/bean&gt;


